QUESTION :
  There are & thieves.
  
  They steal diamonds from diamond merchant and ran awayin jungle.
  
  While running night sets in and they decide to rest in jungle.
  
  When everybody was asleep, two of them decide to to distribute diamond among themselves and run away.
  
  So they start distributing but they find one extra diamond so they decide to wake up the third thief.
  
  when these three divide among themselves they find one extra again and again they wake up the fourth one. 
  
  Again one is spare.
  
  5th woke up...Still one extra!!
  
  Woke up the sixth one again one extra.
  
  now 7th one wake up and they distribute agin and this time it is distributed equally.
  
  How many diamonds in total did they steal ?
